      <title>欧元区生产率令人失望使欧洲央行面临的挑战更加复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/disappointing-euro-area-productivity-complicates-ecb-s-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区生产率在第二季度几乎没有改善，再次未达到欧洲央行的预期——这对其将通胀率恢复到2%的努力是一个打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/disappointing-euro-area-productivity-complicates-ecb-s-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 07:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲最大银行标准银行称工行利润下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/biggest-african-lender-standard-bank-says-profit-dips-on-icbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准银行集团有限公司是资产规模最大的非洲银行，该公司表示，由于其与中国最大银行的合资企业的收益几乎减少了一半，上半年利润下降了 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/biggest-african-lender-standard-bank-says-profit-dips-on-icbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 07:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾央行因消费衰退下调政策利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/philippines-delivers-25-basis-point-rate-cut-as-consumption-ebbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾央行将基准利率下调四分之一个百分点，结束了持续近一年的暂停状态，因为政策制定者试图保持经济发展的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/philippines-delivers-25-basis-point-rate-cut-as-consumption-ebbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 07:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>服务业助力英国经济保持强劲复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/uk-economy-maintains-solid-recovery-in-fillip-for-keir-starmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国经济从去年的经济衰退中保持了稳步复苏的步伐，为首相基尔·斯塔默寻求促进经济增长和修复公共财政提供了强大的经济基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/uk-economy-maintains-solid-recovery-in-fillip-for-keir-starmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 06:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴伐利亚北欧公司和其他医疗保健股因对 Mpox 的担忧而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/virus-detection-medical-stocks-jump-worldwide-on-mpox-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在世界卫生组织宣布非洲迅速蔓延的牛痘疫情为全球卫生紧急事件后，丹麦疫苗开发商 Bavarian Nordic A/S 的股价上涨，其他医疗产品制造商的股价也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/virus-detection-medical-stocks-jump-worldwide-on-mpox-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 05:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
